#- §lEpilogue:§0
§0Thank you for reading this history of the "Nicest City on Civcraft". The city is not dead. It is not abandoned. New players have stepped up to the challange of rebuilding and maintaining thisbeautiful city and will lead it into the 
#- future. With the help of Juz16, Lord_Brenton and Doymand; Aurora will continue on and prosper once again.
